<h3 id="æ€è·¯">æ€è·¯</h3>

<p>è´ªå¿ƒï¼Œæ ¹æ®ç¬¬äºŒä¸ªå…ƒç´ æ’åºï¼Œå‡ç¼“å…¶å¢å¤§çš„é€Ÿåº¦</p>

<h3 id="ä»£ç ">ä»£ç </h3>

<pre><code class="language-c++">class Solution {
public:
    int findLongestChain(vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; pairs) {
        sort(pairs.begin(), pairs.end(), [](auto &amp;a, auto &amp;b){return a[1] &lt; b[1];});
        int res = 1, min = pairs[0][1], n = pairs.size();
        for(int i = 1; i &lt; n; i++){
            if(pairs[i][0] &gt; min){
                res++;
                min = pairs[i][1];
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
};
</code></pre>

<h3 id="æ”¶è·">æ”¶è·</h3>

<p>è¯„è®ºåŒºç”¨dpçš„è§£ï¼š</p>

<p>å¯¹pairs[0]æ’åºï¼Œi = 0:n-1 éå†vectorï¼Œè¿‡ç¨‹ä¸­ j = i-1:0 éå†æ›´æ–°dp[i]ï¼Œ å¯å…¥é“¾åˆ™dp[i] = max(dp[i],1+dp[j])</p>
